</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【開箱】《Elden Ring》艾爾登法環限定版，瑪蓮妮亞 23cm 模型 + 豐富內容逐樣睇</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/02/28/eldenringspecialedition/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=eldenringspecialedition</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Mon, 28 Feb 2022 14:08:20 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1088360</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>由 FromSoftware 開發的動作 RPG《Elden Ring》（艾爾登法環）已經推出。這款遊戲延續了 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>由 FromSoftware 開發的動作 RPG《Elden Ring》（艾爾登法環）已經推出。這款遊戲延續了過往《Dark Souls》、《Bloodborne》經典玩法、世界觀設定與恐佈的氣氛，採用開放世界玩法，角色自訂育成要素更強，而且還可騎乘靈馬走遍各地。而香港 Bandai Namco 也引入了遊戲限定版，內有米凱拉的鋒刃「瑪蓮妮亞」的角色模型，造工相當細緻，就等小編以下同大家一齊開箱。</p><p>《Elden Ring》（艾爾登法環）限定版目可說是非常搶手，打開包裝後可看到有兩個非常精美的紙盒，其中一個裝有遊戲與畫集，而另一個豪華紙盒則是可作模型背景用的外盒。此盒有 30cm 高，打開看到今次限定版的主角，米凱拉的鋒刃「瑪蓮妮亞」角色模型。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0004-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088363" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0004-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0004-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0004-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0004-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0005-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088364" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0005-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0005-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0005-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0005-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>「瑪蓮妮亞」模型高 23 公分，造工十分細緻，原作上色有極具質感的光澤，而頭部的頭盔、手臂都相當有金屬感。整隻模型沒有可動部位，用家可把寶劍套入瑪蓮妮亞手中。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0015-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088365" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0015-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0015-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0015-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0015-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0021-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088366" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0021-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0021-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0016.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088367" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0016-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0016-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0016-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0016.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0017-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088368" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0017-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0017-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0017-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0017-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0019-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088369" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0019-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0019-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0019-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0019-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>模型的座架質感、上色也相當有遊戲的氣氛。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0018-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088370" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0018-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0018-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0018-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0018-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>配上寶劍，也可放置於跟來的豪華紙盒中，可作為非常美觀的擺設。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0020-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088371" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0020-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0020-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0020-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0020-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0023-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0023-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0023-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0023-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0023-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0033-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088373" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0033-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0033-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0033-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0033-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>遊戲方面，限定版跟來了 《Elden Ring》 PS4 行貨實體版遊戲，另外具有精緻鐵盒，鐵盒裡面的背景紙張都印有遊戲場景圖案。隨限定版也跟來遊戲聲軌數碼版的兌換號碼。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0006-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088374" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0006-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0006-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0006-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0006-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0008-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088375" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0008-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0008-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0008-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0008-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0007-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088376" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0007-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0007-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0007-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0007-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0009-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088377" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0009-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0009-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0009-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0009-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>最後要留意這本 40 頁精美美術畫集，硬紙皮封面的入面，印刷了遊戲人物、敵人角色、場景的設定畫，值得收藏。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0010-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088378" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0010-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0010-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0010-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0010-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0011-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088379" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0011-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0011-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0011-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0011-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0013-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088380" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0013-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0013-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0013-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0013-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0012-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088381" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0012-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0012-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0012-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0012-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>發售日期：2022 年 2 月 25 日</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0025-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1088382" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0025-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0025-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0025-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/02/unwire0025-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
